wiki.summary: Brent Faiyaz is back with a new single called “Mercedes.” He is laying out the less-sunny side of what a relationship with him is really like on “Mercedes.” Faiyaz describes how the fancy baubles like the song’s titular car can’t conceal the lonely nights and paranoia over being used that come with being an R&B superstar. Read more on Last.fm.
